### Create a new shelter
POST http://localhost:5000/api/shelters
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "New Shelter",
  "address": "1234 Pet Lane",
  "phoneNumber": "123-456-7890"
}

### Get all shelters
GET http://localhost:5000/api/shelters

### Get a specific shelter by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/shelters/1

### Update a shelter
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/shelters/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Updated Shelter",
  "address": "5678 Animal Ave",
  "phoneNumber": "098-765-4321"
}

### Delete a shelter
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/shelters/1